lead_paragraph: Ireland flyhalf Paddy Jackson and his Ulster team mate Stuart Olding have denied any wrongdoing after police confirmed they had been arrested over allegations of sexual offences.

headline.print_headline: Ireland's Jackson Questioned Over Sexual Offence Allegations
headline.main: Ireland's Jackson Questioned Over Sexual Offence Allegations

snippet: Ireland flyhalf Paddy Jackson and his Ulster team mate Stuart Olding have denied any wrongdoing after police confirmed they had been arrested over allegations of sexual offences....
